    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Physical works, such as drawings and written documents, that were the result of a competition, particularly an artistic or architectural competition in which various applicants vie for a prize or for the assignment of a contract to create the finished work. For the event of the competition, use "competitions (events)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
